<div dir="ltr">Jeff and I iterated a bit off-list and opal/util/path.c in tonight&#39;s trunk tarball (1.9a1r30255) works for all of my systems.<div>With the help of Jeff&#39;s recently-enhanced test/util/opal_path_nfs.c I was able to verify that NFS mounts are now correctly identified on the *BSD systems (and still correct on Linux, Mac OSX, and Solaris).<br>
